<p><strong>Latency matters:</strong> Luna is fastest because it is optimized for streaming, real-time classification, and throughput. Sol is slowest because it performs more internal reasoning. For interactive user-facing workloads, Luna is also cheaper <em>and</em> faster — but only if it's capable enough for your task. This is the key routing decision.</p>

